he Olympics\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Observing the world through a small window, Yiwu, known as the \\\"world's supermarket,\\\" is showcasing the achievements of Chinese manufacturing since its reform and opening-up.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1939, \"end\": 1943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.754399516165242e-34, \"text\": \"Yiwu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\"}, {\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999919887159, \"rank\": 6.50764858728442e-09, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"a small window\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"world's supermarket\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"the achievements\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"its reform\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"opening-up\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the small decorations, Olympic mascots and souvenirs all over Paris to various sportswear, sports equipment and digital screens at the Olympic venues, products that are \\\"made in China\\\" and \\\"made in Yiwu, China\\\" are everywhere.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2138, \"end\": 2143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.623926736400958e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999963217050555, 