d export along the industrial chain.\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the business model\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"individual enterprises\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"an industrial ecosystem model\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"the upstream and downstream design\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"manufacturing\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"sales\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2919}, {\"ngram\": \"export\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"the industrial chain\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's manufacturing industry, represented by Yiwu's manufacturing, has iterated and upgraded, with independent brands sprouting up and gradually achieving \\\"high-quality overseas expansion.\\\"\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999963217050555, \"rank\": 3.6782326025870354e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 3007, \"end\": 3011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.754399516165242e-34, \"text\": \"Yiwu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"independent brands\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3079}, {\"ngram\": \"high-quality overseas expansion\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smart home appliances, new energy vehicles and high-end and professional equipment are shipped from Chinese ports to global markets, marking an impressive transformation from the \\\"world's factory.\\\"\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3153, \"end\": 3158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re