.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chinese economy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Economy_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Economy_of_China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\\"growth miracle\", \"from\": 4798, \"to\": 4815}, {\"ngram\": \"developing countries\", \"from\": 4820, \"to\": 4840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The high-quality development of the manufacturing sector has been the \\\"anchor\\\" in the rapid development of the Chinese economy.\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4954, \"end\": 4969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Economy_of_China\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chinese economy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Economy_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Economy_of_China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The high-quality development\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4871}, {\"ngram\": \"the manufacturing sector\", \"from\": 4875, \"to\": 4899}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"anchor\", \"from\": 4909, \"to\": 4920}, {\"ngram\": \"the rapid development\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 4946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to China's National Bureau of Statistics, in the first half of the year, the added value of major industrial enterprises nationwide grew by 6 percent year on year, with the added value of the manufacturing sector rising by 6.5 percent, outpacing the overall growth of industries by 0.5 percentage point.\", \"from\": 4972, \"to\": 5285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4985, \"end\": 4990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999963217050555, \"rank\": 3.6782326025870354e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Statistics\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5022}, {\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 5027, \"to\": 5041}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\